Package dbAPI

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IColumn
    An interface that represents a column in a database table
    IDatabase
    An interface that represents a database
    IDatabaseHelper
    An interface that represents a generic database for specific database APIs
    It's supposed to link between a specific database type and it's API, and this generic API
    Should be implemented for each database type
    IDatabaseReader
    An interface that represents a reader that reads rows from the database
    IRow
    An interface that represents a row in a database
    ITable
    An interface that represents a table in a database
